CLARK v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 25,

September Term, 1960.]

Decided October 13, 1960.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott and Horney, JJ.

PER Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from a second denial of post conviction relief is denied for the reasons stated by the court below.
